------------- Itinerary 01 -------------
Day 01
    Pickup From Airport & Return to Anuradhapura & check-in to Hotel

    Authentic Sri Lankan Lunch 
    Overnight stay at lake front hotel at anuradhapura with half board basis.

Day 02    
    Take Breakfirst and Exploreing anuradhapura

    Visiting Places.
        1. Sri Maha Bodhi  
        2. Ruwanwelisaya  
        3. Jetavanaramaya 
        4. Abhayagiri Dagoba 
        5. Kuttam Pokuna Twin Ponds

    Lunch At Anuradhapura Restudent
    Depart from Anuradhapura to Trincomalee.
    Overnight Stay At Trincomalee beach front hotel with half board basis.

Day 03
    Take Breakfirst at Trinco hotel and Explaring Trincomalee.

    Visiting Places.
        1. Koneswaram Temple
        2. Trincomalee Harbour Visit
        3. Relaxing at Nilaveli/Marbel Beach at evening.
    
    Seafood Lunch at Trincomalee Restudent
    Overnight stay at Troncomalee beach front hotel with Half Board Basis

Day 04
    Take breackfirst at trincomalee hotel and return to Sigiriya.

    Visiting places.
        1. Sigiriya Rock Fortress
        2. Dambulla Cave Temple
    
    Sri Lankan Lunch at sigiriya restudent
    Depart For Kandy & Check-in to Kandy hotel with half board basis

Day 05
    Take Breackfirst at kandy hotel and explore Kandy.

    Visiting Places.
        1. Temple of the Sacred Tooth Relic
        2. Kandy Lake 
        3. Kandy View Point
    
    Lunch at Local Restudent & Departure to Airport
    Fairwell & say good bye!


